== UDK2014 IHV Driver Developer Release (UDK2014.IHV) ==

Reduced distribution of the [[UDK2014]] specifically for independent hardware vendors (IHV) creating UEFI drivers.
* EDK II [[BaseTools]] for Windows and Linux
* [[MdeModulePkg]]
* [[MdePkg]]
* [http://sourceforge.net/projects/edk2/files/UDK2014_Releases/UDK2014/UDK2014.IHV-ReleaseNotes.txt/download Release Notes] and Documentation

This subset of packages is designed to be used with the [[UEFI Driver Wizard]].

== Setup and Configuration ==

# Download the UDK2014 IHV package ([http://sourceforge.net/projects/edk2/files/UDK2014_Releases/UDK2014/UDK2014.IHV.zip/download UDK2014.IHV]).
# Unzip [http://sourceforge.net/projects/edk2/files/UDK2014_Releases/UDK2014/UDK2014.IHV.zip/download UDK2014.IHV] into a workspace directory (example: C:\FW\UDK2014.IHV)
# Unzip the BaseTools ZIP file into the workspace directory
# Open a Visual Studio Command Prompt and run edksetup.bat in the workspace directory

